name: Literal Shit - Monochrome taster
description:
As part of the Literal Shit [1000 mints] project we will be giving out sample shits to those we look up to in the space. 

These are monochromatic with some delicate retouching on the shit to make it pop a bit.

This cannot be bought on primary, and will only available through the secondary market from friends of LitShitDAO that have been gifted.
